    },
    {
      "end": 50.119998931884766,
      "text": "I be walking dark paths, I be walking light paths, I be walking things in judgement inside with my past in tow.",
      "start": 41.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 63.459999084472656,
      "text": "I try not to make mistakes again, but sometimes you're just fucking with my head when you just take my heart out.",
      "start": 50.119998931884766
    },
    {
      "end": 69.33999633789062,
      "text": "Throw away light and ground right in front of me, and do you have a soul yet?",
      "start": 63.459999084472656
    },
    {
      "end": 81.9000015258789,
      "text": "Because I surrender to all your hate, I won't fight back.",
      "start": 69.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 96.4800033569336,
      "text": "I surrender, I surrender all I need for you.",
      "start": 82.9000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 108.69999694824219,
      "text": "I surrender all I get for you.",
      "start": 99.69999694824219
    },
    {
      "end": 121.31999969482422,
      "text": "Sometimes I look back when things weren't the way we thought they'd be.",
      "start": 112.62000274658203
    },
    {
      "end": 133.86000061035156,
      "text": "How many times did you want me to give up my rights to all the love that was supposed to be for me, baby?",
      "start": 122.87999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 138.33999633789062,
      "text": "But now I see it's all about you and me.",
      "start": 133.86000061035156
